cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SI, cs.CL

The paper deals with discriminant analysis for speaker verification, which falls under the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also involves statistical learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. The proposed method involves simultaneous diagonalization (SD) of covariance matrices, which is a common technique in spectral clustering (cs.SD).
